TREATMENT OF WASTEWATER IN TEKU HOSPITAL
August 20, 2022
Health Environment and Climate Action Foundation (Hecaf360) is one of the renowned organisations which is committed to clean, green and environmentally safe healthcare. In the month of June, it conducted a demonstration of electrochemical treatment technology and evaluation test for the treatment of hospital wastewater in Teku hospital. Our Supreme Associates Traders, leader in water and wastewater treatment, sponsored Hecaf360 by providing different facilities required during the treatment process.
We are a team of certified water treatment professionals who have been active in the market since 2010 A.D. In the field of water treatment, our key experts have more than 20 years of experience.

Health Environment and Climate Action Foundation (Hecaf360) is one of the renowned organisations which is committed to clean, green and environmentally safe healthcare. In the month of June, it conducted a demonstration of electrochemical treatment technology and evaluation test for the treatment of hospital wastewater in Teku hospital. Our Supreme Associates Traders, leader in water and wastewater treatment, sponsored Hecaf360 by providing different facilities required during the treatment process.
We are a team of certified water treatment professionals who have been active in the market since 2010 A.D. In the field of water treatment, our key experts have more than 20 years of experience.
